Maybe of all time.

1358
01:23:45,454 --> 01:23:47,556
而我不会开一枪
And I'm not gonna fire a single shot.

1359
01:23:48,624 --> 01:23:50,393
我将用言语来打这场仗
I'm gonna fight it with words.

1360
01:23:52,095 --> 01:23:56,399
他们必须仔细权衡每一个字
And they have to count every single one of them.

1361
01:23:56,532 --> 01:23:59,135
所以说话要言简意赅，
So say what you mean,

1362
01:23:59,268 --> 01:24:00,636
言出必行
mean what you say.

1363
01:24:02,371 --> 01:24:04,873
我需要那个在我院子里露营的人
I need the guy who camped out in my yard.

1364
01:24:05,007 --> 01:24:05,974
你明白吗？
You understand?

1365
01:24:16,119 --> 01:24:17,653
让我们为那些生活在
And let us pray

1366
01:24:17,786 --> 01:24:19,888
极权主义黑暗中的人
for the salvation of those who live

1367
01:24:20,022 --> 01:24:22,158
祈祷救赎
in that totalitarian darkness.

1368
01:24:23,359 --> 01:24:26,028
让我们祈祷他们能发现
Let us pray that they will discover

1369
01:24:26,162 --> 01:24:27,996
认识上帝的喜悦
the joy of knowing God

1370
01:24:28,697 --> 01:24:31,934
让我们意识到，当他们那些未经选举的领导人
and let us be aware that while their unelected leaders

1371
01:24:32,067 --> 01:24:34,437
宣扬国家至上，
preach the supremacy of the State,

1372
01:24:34,570 --> 01:24:38,207
宣称国家凌驾于个人之上，
declare its omnipotence over individual man

1373
01:24:38,341 --> 01:24:40,276
并预言最终将统治
and predict its eventual domination

1374
01:24:40,409 --> 01:24:42,345
地球上所有的人民时，
of all the peoples of the Earth,

1375
01:24:42,478 --> 01:24:46,048
他们就是现代世界邪恶的焦点
they are the focus of evil in the modern world.

1376
01:24:47,516 --> 01:24:48,784
正如C.S.刘易斯
It was C.S. Lewis,

1377
01:24:48,951 --> 01:24:53,222
在他出色的《地狱来信》中所写：
who in his magnificent,Screwtape Letters wrote,

1378
01:24:53,356 --> 01:24:55,891
"最大的邪恶并非产生于
"The greatest evil is not done

1379
01:24:56,024 --> 01:24:59,528
狄更斯笔下
那些肮脏的犯罪窝点，
in those sordid dens of crime that Dickens loved to paint

1380
01:24:59,695 --> 01:25:04,733
也不是在集中营和劳改营中产生
nor is it done in the concentration camps and labor camps.

1381
01:25:04,900 --> 01:25:08,271
在那里，我们只看到了它的最终结果
In them, we see its final result.

1382
01:25:08,437 --> 01:25:10,873
但它的构想和指令
But it is conceived and ordered

1383
01:25:11,039 --> 01:25:15,378
来自于干净、铺着地毯
温暖、灯火通明的办公室，
in clear, carpeted, warmed, and well-lighted offices

1384
01:25:15,544 --> 01:25:19,348
来自于那些衣冠楚楚
指甲修剪整齐的安静男人，
by quiet men with white collars and cut fingernails

1385
01:25:19,515 --> 01:25:21,584
他们不需要提高嗓门，
who do not need to raise their voices,

1386
