而是用温和的语调
谈论兄弟情谊和和平"
but speak in soothing tones of brotherhood and peace."

1387
01:25:26,455 --> 01:25:30,359
要警惕忽视历史事实的诱惑，
Beware the temptation to ignore the facts of history,

1388
01:25:30,526 --> 01:25:34,062
以及邪恶帝国的侵略冲动
and the aggressive impulses of an evil empire.

1389
01:25:36,064 --> 01:25:36,965
没错！
Yes!

1390
01:25:41,870 --> 01:25:44,473
我认为总统的话有点不负责任
I think the President's words were a little irresponsible.

1391
01:25:44,640 --> 01:25:47,576
我们现在最不需要的
就是让冷战升温
Last thing we need to do is heat this Cold War up.

1392
01:25:47,743 --> 01:25:50,246
虽然总统今晚显然认为...
While the President clearly thought tonight...

1393
01:25:50,379 --> 01:25:52,348
这些人怎么回事？
What is wrong with these people?

1394
01:25:52,481 --> 01:25:54,149
我是说，他们到底站在谁那边？
I mean, whose side are they on, anyway?

1395
01:25:54,283 --> 01:25:58,187
哦，亲爱的，你不能太在意那些
Oh, honey, you can't pay any attention to that.

1396
01:25:58,321 --> 01:26:01,824
但我必须在意
大多数国民都在关注他们
But I have to. Most of the country is paying attention to them.

1397
01:26:01,957 --> 01:26:05,661
嗯，如果你觉得
那让他们大为光火，你就等着瞧吧
Well, if you think that got their undies in a wad, you just wait.

1398
01:26:06,662 --> 01:26:10,333
我们已经阻止核战争三十多年了
We have prevented nuclear war for more than three decades.

1399
01:26:10,466 --> 01:26:14,470
