我们不能仅仅依靠
Recently, however, it has become clear we cannot rely solely

1400
01:26:14,603 --> 01:26:18,006
进攻性报复来维持和平
on offensive retaliation to maintain peace.

1401
01:26:18,140 --> 01:26:20,476
我呼吁科学界，
I call upon the scientific community,

1402
01:26:20,609 --> 01:26:22,878
那些给我们核武器的人，
those who gave us nuclear weapons

1403
01:26:23,011 --> 01:26:28,217
现在将他们的伟大才能
用于人类和世界和平的事业
to turn their great talents now to the cause of mankind and world peace.

1404
01:26:28,351 --> 01:26:30,986
建造这个防御性的"导弹盾牌"，
To build this defensive,"missile shield,"

1405
01:26:31,153 --> 01:26:34,857
使这些武器失去作用和过时
rendering these weapons impotent and obsolete.

1406
01:26:35,023 --> 01:26:36,659
如果我们采取这些措施...
If we take these measures...

1407
01:26:36,825 --> 01:26:40,062
他从1940年他主演的一部电影中
得到这个想法
He got the idea from a movie he starred in, in 1940.

1408
01:26:40,929 --> 01:26:45,701
而且随着经济的繁荣
他现在有钱可以花了
And with his economy booming, he now had the money to spend.

1409
01:26:47,270 --> 01:26:48,637
但这东西并不存在
But it didn't exist.

1410
01:26:48,771 --> 01:26:49,738
小细节而已
Small detail.

1411
01:26:50,939 --> 01:26:53,041
- 小细节？ - 让我们这么说吧
- Small detail? - Let's just say

1412
01:26:53,175 --> 01:26:55,978
他一如既往地乐观
he was characteristically optimistic.

1413
01:26:56,111 --> 01:26:57,480
所以他是在撒谎
So he was lying.

1414
01:26:57,613 --> 01:26:59,147
来，吃点东西
Here. Eat something.

1415
01:26:59,282 --> 01:27:00,816
维克托·彼得洛维奇，它根本不存在
Viktor Petrovich, it didn't exist.

1416
01:27:00,949 --> 01:27:02,184
这只是科幻小说
It was science fiction.

1417
01:27:02,318 --> 01:27:04,987
但导弹，导弹是存在的！
But the missiles, missiles did!

1418
01:27:05,120 --> 01:27:06,322
没关系
Doesn't matter.

1419
01:27:07,055 --> 01:27:09,558
十字军正在采取行动
The Crusader was making his move.

1420
01:27:09,692 --> 01:27:11,193
我们知道这一点
And we knew it.

1421
01:27:14,363 --> 01:27:15,764
然后发生了一些事
And then something happened.

1422
01:27:18,133 --> 01:27:19,201
比如什么？
Like what?

1423
01:27:36,184 --> 01:27:39,755
大韩航空，你们正在苏联领空
Korean Airlines, you are in Soviet airspace.

1424
01:27:39,888 --> 01:27:41,290
立即离开
Move out now.

1425
01:27:53,669 --> 01:27:55,237
指挥部，没有回应
Command, there is no response.

1426
01:27:55,404 --> 01:27:57,072
似乎是商业航班
Appears to be commercial flight.

1427
01:27:57,239 --> 01:27:59,542
- 击落它- 你确定吗？
-  Shoot it down. -  Are you sure?

1428
01:27:59,708 --> 01:28:01,477
我看到闪烁的指示灯
I see flashing indicators.

1429
01:28:01,644 --> 01:28:04,313
- 击落它- 收到
-  Shoot it down. -  Copy that.

1430
01:28:24,600 --> 01:28:26,068
一架民航客机？
A civilian airliner?

1431
01:28:26,234 --> 01:28:27,703
CIA间谍飞机
CIA spy plane.

1432
01:28:27,870 --> 01:28:29,438
他们已经被反复警告过了
They were warned repeatedly.

1433
01:28:29,572 --> 01:28:31,507
那是一架商业航班！
It was a commercial flight!

1434
01:28:31,640 --> 01:28:33,609
两百六十九人
Two hundred and sixty-nine people

1435
01:28:33,776 --> 01:28:35,077
都死了，阿纳托利，
are dead, Anatoly,

1436
01:28:35,243 --> 01:28:36,979
其中包括我们的一位国会议员！
including one of our congressman!

1437
01:28:37,112 --> 01:28:39,281
- 乔治...- 你越界了
-  George... - You crossed a line.

1438
01:28:49,692 --> 01:28:53,529
冷战对手之间的紧张局势继续升级
Tensions between the Cold War adversaries continue to escalate.

1439
01:28:53,696 --> 01:28:56,432
里根总统称之为野蛮行径
President Reagan called it an act of barbarism.

1440
01:28:56,599 --> 01:28:59,635
北约军队在整个欧洲保持警戒状态
NATO forces remain on alert across Europe.

1441
01:28:59,802 --> 01:29:01,970
国内外许多人都担心
Many are concerned at home and abroad

1442
01:29:02,137 --> 01:29:05,307
这些行动使美国和苏联
that these actions bring the United States and the Soviet Union

1443
01:29:05,474 --> 01:29:08,343
离直接军事冲突更近了一步
a step closer to a direct military conflict.

1444
01:29:09,878 --> 01:29:11,614
三周后，
And three weeks later,

1445
01:29:11,780 --> 01:29:15,784
我们的雷达系统检测到了
不可想象的情况
our radar systems detected the unthinkable.

1446
01:29:18,053 --> 01:29:21,056
引发了一系列令人恐惧的反应
Triggering a terrifying response of action.

1447
01:29:24,259 --> 01:29:27,229
- 这不是演习
- 我们有确认吗？
- This is not a drill. - Do we have confirmation on this?

1448
01:29:27,362 --> 01:29:28,997
苏联正在加热六个地点
Soviets are heating up six sites.

1449
01:29:29,131 --> 01:29:30,866
那意味着1800万美国人的生命
That's 18 million,American lives.

1450
01:29:30,999 --> 01:29:32,134
他们以为我们要发射，先生
They think we're launching, sir.

1451
01:29:32,267 --> 01:29:33,469
准备进入一级战备状态
Prepare for DEFCON 1.

1452
01:29:33,602 --> 01:29:35,571
我需要确认
I need confirmation.

1453
01:29:35,704 --> 01:29:39,842
总统先生，如果这是真的
我们没时间确认了
Mr. President, if this is real, we won't have time for confirmation.

1454
01:29:44,012 --> 01:29:45,581
我们需要一个决定
We need a decision.

1455
01:30:48,511 --> 01:30:50,479
他们正在中止，先生
他们正在撤退
They're aborting, sir. They're standing down.

1456
01:30:50,613 --> 01:30:52,881
好的，先生我会通知他们的
Okay, sir. I'll let them know.

1457
01:30:53,015 --> 01:30:55,651
我们差点就...
We're that close.

1458
01:30:55,784 --> 01:30:58,587
看来是一群鹅触发了雷达的正面反应
Looks like a flock of geese triggered a positive radar hit.

1459
01:30:58,721 --> 01:30:59,922
- 天啊- 啊
- Ah, Jesus. - Ah.

1460
01:31:01,223 --> 01:31:02,625
我简直不敢相信
I can't believe it.

1461
01:31:04,493 --> 01:31:07,796
冷战正处于全面进行中
The Cold War was in full swing.

1462
01:31:07,963 --> 01:31:11,767
十字军战士知道
他必须继续对我们施压，
The Crusader knew he had to keep the pressure on us,

1463
01:31:11,934 --> 01:31:14,903
但要确保不再出现错误
but making sure there were no more mistakes.

1464
01:31:16,138 --> 01:31:20,308
但在他恢复对我们的讨伐之前，
But before he could resume his crusade against us,

1465
01:31:20,475 --> 01:31:22,511
他必须面对他的选民
he would have to face his voters.

1466
01:31:23,612 --> 01:31:28,150
让我们这么说吧
并不是所有人都认为他是正确的选择
And let's just say, not everyone thought he was the right choice.

1467
01:31:38,160 --> 01:31:40,495
啊道貌岸然的人
Ah. Goody two-shoes.

1468
01:32:47,830 --> 01:32:51,634
蒙代尔先生的民调支持率
一直在稳步上升
Mr. Mondale's poll numbers have been steadily rising.

1469
01:32:51,800 --> 01:32:55,403
