Concerns have been raised as the President has stumbled,

1470
01:32:55,570 --> 01:32:57,539
他在上一场辩论中显得疲惫不堪
appearing tired in the last debate.

1471
01:32:57,706 --> 01:33:00,208
里根总统很可能最终成为
President Reagan could very well end up

1472
01:33:00,342 --> 01:33:02,110
一位只当一届的总统
a one-term president.

1473
01:33:05,513 --> 01:33:07,582
那么，你如何调整通货膨胀率，呃，
So how do you adjust for inflation, uh,

1474
01:33:07,716 --> 01:33:10,786
在6%到12%的预测区间内？
between the six and twelve percent projections?

1475
01:33:10,919 --> 01:33:12,788
嗯，你知道，
Well, you know,

1476
01:33:13,722 --> 01:33:17,225
随着四百万...新增就业岗位的增加...
that with the adding of four million...

1477
01:33:21,229 --> 01:33:23,398
三百万新增就业岗位
Three million new jobs

1478
01:33:23,531 --> 01:33:26,401
以及失业率的变化...
and the rate of unemployment being...

1479
01:33:31,874 --> 01:33:32,941
好了
Okay.

1480
01:33:33,075 --> 01:33:35,410
停下停下
Stop. Stop.

1481
01:33:36,378 --> 01:33:37,713
我需要休息一下
I need a break.

1482
01:33:43,585 --> 01:33:46,254
总统先生，我们真的觉得...
Mr. President, we really feel that...

1483
01:33:46,388 --> 01:33:48,056
我-我们只需要重新来过
w-we just need to do this all over again.

1484
01:33:48,190 --> 01:33:50,292
不我受够了，埃德
No. I've had enough, Ed.

1485
01:33:51,193 --> 01:33:54,897
那个，总-总统先生，我忘了
您最喜欢的电影是什么？
Say, M-Mr. President, I forgot, what's your favorite movie?

1486
01:33:56,098 --> 01:33:57,432
《音乐之声》
The Sound of Music.

1487
01:33:58,433 --> 01:34:00,002
要不您和里根夫人今晚
What do you say, you and Mrs. Reagan

1488
01:34:00,135 --> 01:34:01,670
一起看这部电影怎么样？
get together and watch it tonight?

1489
01:34:01,804 --> 01:34:03,605
放松一下，让头脑平静下来
Relax, calm your mind.

1490
01:34:03,739 --> 01:34:05,073
明天您就能重新振作起来
You'll be back in the saddle tomorrow.

1491
01:34:05,207 --> 01:34:07,442
我们也会准备就绪
And we'll be ready to go.

1492
01:34:07,575 --> 01:34:09,745
